      "text": "Neveens bija no wiſſeem Behrneem/ ko ta irr dſemdejſt/ kaß winan wadditu/ un neveens no wiſſeem Behrneem / ko ta irr uſaudſnaſſi/ kaß winnu pee Rohkas neintu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schiß diwejaß Leetas irr tew notikunſchas/ kaß tad te- wi ſchehſja ? Pohſtiichana un Catreekſchana / un Bads / un Sobbins bija klaht/ kaſtad war- reja tewi cepreezinaht?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawi Bebrui bija pa- mirruschi/ tee gulleja us wiſſahm Eelahuu / ka weens Mescha- Wehrſis Tihſii/ tee bija pilli tahs Bahrsibas ta KU RGA/ tahs Laũatchanas tawa Deewa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz klaufi jelle ſcho/ tu Apbehdiñata un tu Peedseh- ruſt/ bet ne no Wiyna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta faſka taws Kungs/ tas KUNGS un taws Deews/ kaß farwo Lauschu Teefu neſſihs: Redſi/eß xenunu to Breeſmiibas- Biﬀerti no tawas Rohkas/ tahs Meeles ta Biﬀera mannas Bahrsibas/ teiw ne buhs winnu wairs ilgaki dſert.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet es Dohſchu winnu ta- weem Plehfajeem Rohká/ kaß us tawn Dwehſeli fazzija: Lohkajs/ ka michß pahr tew eetam/ un no- leeß tawn Magguru fa ta Sem- me/ un ka weena Eela teem/ kaß us to staiga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Smohſtees/ uſmohſtees/ Apwelz tawn Stipru- mu ak Ziana! apwelz tawas ſkaistas Drehbeg / tu ſwehtajs Pilſtahts Jeruſaleme. Jo eeſch tewis ne nahks wairs nekahds Ne-Apgraiſhts neds Neſchkibſts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Iskrattajs no Pihschleem/ zellees/ apſehdees ak Jeruſale- me! atraiſees no tawa Raſla Saitehm/ tu zeetinata Zianas Meita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta faſka tas KUNGS: Juhs effat welſi pahrdohti/ juhs tapſeet arri bes Naudas at- pestiti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta faſka tas Klungs KUNGS: Wezzõß Laikõß no- gabje manni Landis us Egipti par Swetchineeleem tur miſt/ un Affurs irr tohs bes Wainas apbehdiñajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu/ kaß irr manſcheit? faſka tas KUNGS: Jo man- ni Landis welti irr atkemti/ un winnu Walditaji leek tohs faſkt/ faſka tas KUNGS: un mans Wahrdß tohp bes Mitteſchanas zauru Deenu faimohts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht manni Landis mannu Wahrdn pasihs tai Dec- na/ ka es pats taſefinu/ kaſran- naß/ Rangi/ Es.\n"
    }
  ],
